quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, hulee Joomi mo'on, pellet, dillannde Darngal ngal ko huunde mawnde"
  22,2,"√Ďalnde yi'oton ngal, yejjitoyay kala muyninoowo ko o muyninaynoo kon, fukka kala sowii…óo ko o sowiinoo kon, a yi'ay yim…ďe …ďen no siwri, hara kam…ďe …ďe siwraa, kono Lepte Alla …óen ko sa…ótu…óe"
  22,3,"No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal, o jakka kala Seytaane canndallo"
  22,4,"Winndaama e hoore-makko wonnde pellet, kala weldu…óo e makko pellet, o majjinay mo, o …óowa mo haa ka Lepte Sa'iiri"
  22,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, si tawii on laatike e sikke immorde e immital ngal, pellet, Menen Men Tagii on immorde e mbullaari refti e to…ď…ďere maniiyu, refti e he…ó…óere refti e huyre timmunde tagu e nde wonaa timmunde tagu fii yo Men …ďannginan on, Me…óen √Ďii…ďina ka renngaaji ko Men Muuyi kon haa e happu innaa…óo, refti Men yaltini on ko on booboo…ďe, refti fii yo on yotto sagatalaaku mo'on no e mo'on …ďen …ďe no maaya no e mo'on kadi …ďen …ďe no ruttee faade ka …ďuri jaasude e ngurndan …óam fii wata …ďe anndu …ďaawo ganndal hay e huunde. A yi'ay leydi ndin ko yoorunde si Men jippinii e dow mayri ndiyam …óan ndi dilla ndi ∆īura ndi fu…óina immorde e kala noone woo…óu…óo"
  22,6,"∆äum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurnitay may…ďe …ďen, tawde pellet, ko O Hattan…óo e dow kala huunde. @Corrected"
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, wonnde pellet, Alla immintinay …ďen won…ďe ka genaale"
  22,8,No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wanaa peewal wanaa deftere nur…óunde(jalbunde)
  22,9,"Hofu…óo balaaji mu'un [mawnintinii…óo] fii yo o majjin gaayi Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna oyeere Men mee…óinoyay mo kadi √Ďalnde Darngal Lepte sumoowe ngen"
  22,10,"∆äum ko sabu ko juu…óe maa…óa …óen ardini kon. E wonnde pellet, Alla wonaali Too√Īoowo jeyaa…ďe …ďen"
  22,11,"No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si mo∆ī∆īere he…ďii mo o tabitira sabu …óum si jarrabuyee kadi he…ďii mo o waylitoo e yeeso makko, o hayrii aduna on e Laakara on ko …óum tigi woni hayrere …ďanngunde nden"
  22,12,"Himo rewa gaanin Alla kon ko lorrataa mo e kon ko nafataa mo kadi. ∆äum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], ko …óum woni majjere wo…ó…óunde nden"
  22,13,"Himo rewa on mo lorra muu…óum no …ďuri …ďadaade diini nafa muu…óum kan, bonii welddi…óo bonii kadi wuuridaa…óo"
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla hiMo naada …ďen gom…óin…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji can…ói …óin, pellet, Alla hiMo wa…óa ko O faandii kon. @Corrected"
  22,15,On won…óo no sikka wonnde Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka Laakara; haray yo o fontu …ďoggol faade ka kammu refti o ta∆īa ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko …óen ittay ko tikkini kon
  22,16,"Ko wano nii Men Jippiniri nde Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe. Pellet, Alla hiMo Fewna on Mo O faandii"
  22,17,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óin…ďe e …ďen Yahuudinkoo…ďe e Saabi'iyankoo…ďe e Annasaarankoo…ďe e Majuusinkoo…ďe e …ďen sirkoo…ďe, pellet, Alla O seerndoowo hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal. Pellet, Alla e dow kala huunde ko O Seedii…óo"
  22,18,"Enee a yi'aali, wonndema Alla no sujjannde Mo …ďen won…ďe ka kammuuli e …ďen won…ďe ka leydi, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun e koode …óen e pelle …óen e le…ó…óe …óen e daabeeji …óin e ko …óuu…ói immorde e yim…ďe …ďen, ko …óuu…ói kadi wajibike e mu'un Lepte …óen. Kala mo Alla hoyni haray alanaa mo teddinoowo, pellet Alla hiMo golla ko O Muuyi kon"
  22,19,"∆Āee …óoo …ói…óo ko wennjondir…ďe, …ďe wennjondirii fii Joomi ma…ď…ďe …ďen yeddu…ďe non, ta∆īanoyte …ďe conci immorde e Yiite fatu…óam yuppee ka dow ko'e ma…ď…ďe"
  22,20,Hi…óam honciniree(hayniree) ko woni kon ka deedi ma…ď…ďe e guri …óin kadi
  22,21,No woodani …ďoole immorde e njamndi
  22,22,"Tuma kala …ďe faandii yaltugol nder ton immorde e suno, …ďe ruttee e nder magge, […ďe wi‚Äôanee:] mee…óee Lette sumoowe ngen"
  22,23,"Pellet, Alla naada …ďen gom…óin…ďe …ďe golle mo∆ī∆īi …óin Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji can…ói …óin, …ďe cu…óiree nder ton immorde jawe kanŇče e lu'ulu'uuje koltu ma…ď…ďe on nder ton ko hariire. @Corrected"
  22,24,"∆Āe fewnaama faade e ko laa…ďi immorde e konngol ngol, …ďe fewnaa kadi faade e Laawol Yettiniingol ngol"
  22,25,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe hi…ďe faddaade gaayi Laawol Alla ngol e Juulirde Horminnde nden, nden nde Men wa…óani …óum yim…ďe …ďen, no fota ter √Īii…ďu…óo on e mayre e liigotoo…óo on. Kala faalaa…óo oo√Īorde e mayre too√Īe, Men mee…óinay mo immorde e Lepte muusu…óe"
  22,26,"E tuma nde Men Jippinnoo Ibraahiima nokku Suudu ndun, [Men Daali:] Wata a kafidu e Am hay e huunde, la…ď…ďin Suudu Am ndun fii wanngotoo…ďe …ďen e darotoo…ďe …ďen [juula] e ru∆ī∆īoo…ďe sujja …ďen"
  22,27,"Noddin e yim…ďe …ďen fii Hajju ngun, …ďe aray e maa…óa ko …ďe seppoo…ďe e dow kala …óehiimba reedu, …ďe aray immorde e kala laawol wo…ó…óungol"
  22,28,"Fii yo …ďe seedo nafoore ma…ď…ďe, …ďe jaŇčtoo Innde Alla e nder √Īal…ói anndaa…ói e dow ko O arsiki …ďe kon immorde e muumi neemoraa…ói, √Īaamee e majji, √Īamminon kadi baaso …ďillii…óo on"
  22,29,"Refti yo …ďe ittu tuundi ma…ď…ďe ndin, yo …ďe humnu takke ma…ď…ďe …óen, yo …ďe wanngo Suudu rimdinaa- dun"
  22,30,"∆äum [ko yamira…óon], kala mawnin…óo Hurumji Alla …óin haray …óum ko mo∆ī∆īere makko ka Joomi makko. Daginanaama on neemoraa…ói …óin, si wonaa kon ko janngaa e taweede mo'on, wo…ó…óitee so…ďudi …óin immorde e sanamuuji, wo…ó…óito…óon kadi konngol fenaande ngol"
  22,31,"Newanii…ďe Alla …ďe wanaali sirkanoo…ďe Mo, kala sirkan…óo Alla no wa'ita wa si o uuyu immorde ka kammu sonndu biftoo mo maa…óum henndu ndun ruuyida e makko [na…ďa] e nokkure wo…ó…óunde"
  22,32,"∆äum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo hollii] kala mawnin…óo Maandeeji Alla …óin, pellet …óum, ko e kulol …ďer…óe …óen jeyaa"
  22,33,"No woodani on e majji nafaaji haa e dummunne innaa…óo, refti nokku majji on ko ka Suudu Ndimuru"
  22,34,"Men wa…óanii kala mofte laawol fii yo …ďe jaŇčto Innde Alla e dow ko O arsiki …ďe kon immorde e muumi neemoraa…ói. Rewetee…óo mon On ko Rewetee…óo Gooto ko Kanko jebbilato…óon, weltinir …óoftii…ďe …ďen"
  22,35,"∆Āen [taw…ďe] si Alla jaŇčtaama …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen hulay, e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen e dow kon ko he…ďi …ďe e √Īinnoo…ďe Julde nden hi…ďe nafka go…ó…óum e ko Men arsiki …ďe kon"
  22,36,"E geloo…ói [fay…ói] …óin Men wa…óanii on …ói jeyaa…óum e Maandeeji Alla no woodani on e majji mo∆ī∆īere, jaŇčtee Innde Alla e dow majji ko …ói saffinii…ói si becce majji …óen yanii haray √Īaamee immorde e majji √Īamminon kadi yonndinii…óo e wee…ďitotoo…óo, ko wano nii, Men eltirani on …ói belajo'o onon on jarnay"
  22,37,"Hewtoytaa Alla tebbuuli majji wanaa ∆īii∆īe majji kadi, kono hewtoy Mo kulol ngol immorde e mo'on. Ko wano nii O eltani on …ói fii yo on mawnin Alla e dow ko O fewni on kon, weltin mo∆ī∆īin…ďe …ďen"
  22,38,"Pellet, Alla O solnanay(dunyanay) …ďen gom…óin…ďe, pellet, Alla O yi…óaa kala hodoowo heewu…óo geddi"
  22,39,"DuŇčanaama …ďen wonaa…ďe ha…ďeede [yo…ďtagol] sabu kam…ďe ko …ďe too√Īaa…ďe, pellet, Alla ko O Hattan…óo e dow wallugol …ďe"
  22,40,"∆Āen yaltinaa…ďe ka galleeji mu'un ko aldaa e goo- nga si wanaa fii tun …ďe wi'ii: \"Joomi amen ko Alla\". Sinndo wanaano Alla du√Īirde yim…ďe …ďen yoga e ma…ď…ďe yoga, yirbinteno rewir…ói ruhbaaniyankoo…ďe …ďen e rewir…ói Annasaara en e rewir…ói Alyahuuda en e Juulir…óe …óe Innde Alla jaŇčtetee e nder mu'un ko heewi. ma Alla wallu …ďen walloo…ďe Mo, pellet, Alla ko O Dolnu…óo Teddu…óo"
  22,41,∆Āen taw…ďe si Men newinanii …ďe ka leydi …ďe √Īinnay Julde nden …ďe totta askaal on …ďe yamira ko mo∆ī∆īi kon …ďe ha…óa ko boni kon. Ko Alla woodani …ďattane fiyakuuji …óin
  22,42,"Si …ďe fennii ma, haray gom…óii fenniino ado ma…ď…ďe yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen e Aadinkoo…ďe …ďen e Samuudinkoo…ďe …ďen"
  22,43,E yim…ďe Ibraahiima …ďen e yim…ďe Luutu …ďen
  22,44,"E yim…ďe Madyana …ďen Muusaa kadi fennaama, Mi nennani yeddu…ďe …ďen refti Mi nanngi …ďe, ko honno yagginngol Am ngol wonirnoo"
  22,45,"No foti hewde e Saare nde Men halki …óum tawi ko nde too√Īunde, hara hinde ajjii e hoore kippudiiji mayre, e woyndu yirbundu e hu…ďeere toowunde [eggaande]"
  22,46,"Enee, hara …ďee yahaali ka leydi sakko laatanoo…ďe …ďer…óe …ďe haqqilira …óe, maa…óum noppi …ďe nanira …ói? Pellet, [ko woni kon] wanaa gite …óen wumi, kono ko …ďer…óe wonu…óe …óen e nder becce …óen wumi"
  22,47,"Hi…ďe …óa…ď…ďire yaccinaneede Lepte …óen, [e …óum le] Alla lunndataako fodoore Makko nden. Pellet √Īallal ka Joomi maa…óa ko wano duu…ďi wuluure no limorton non"
  22,48,"No foti heewde e saare nde Mi nennani …óum hara kayre ko nde too√Īunde, refti Mi nannginde ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde nden"
  22,49,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, anndee min ko mi jertinoowo on …ďanngu…óo"
  22,50,∆Āen gom…óin…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īi …óin no woodani …ďe haforanal e arsike teddu…óo
  22,51,"∆Āen yaccii…ďe [fii bonnugol] e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe ronkinaa [Men] ko …ďen …óon woni yim…ďe Jahiimaawe ngen"
  22,52,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo wanaa kadi Annabaajo si wanaa si o janngii Seytaane werloto e nder janki makko kin. Alla itta ko Seytaane werlii kon, refti Alla tabintina Aayeeje Makko …óen. Alla ko O Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  22,53,"Fii yo O wa…óu ko Seytaane werlotoo ko njarraboye wonannde …ďen …ďe nawnaare woni ka …ďer…óe mu'un e …ďe …ďer…óe mu'un yoori …ďen. Pellet, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen …ďe wonii e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  22,54,"Fii yo …ďen okkaa…ďe Ganndal ngal anndu pellet, ko [Alqur'aanaare nden woni] Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi maa…óa …ďe gom…óina nde, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yankinanoo …óum. Pellet Alla Fewnay …ďen gom…óin…ďe faade e Laawol Focciingol"
  22,55,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe seerataa hi…ďe e nder sikke [fii Alqur'aana] haa Darngal ngal ara e ma…ď…ďe e juhayee maa…óum ara e ma…ď…ďe Lepte √Ďalaande sa…ótunde"
  22,56,"Laamu ngun nden √Ďalnde ko Alla heeranii O √Ďaawoyay hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, …ďen gom…óin…ďe …ďe golli ko mo∆ī∆īi …óin hi…ďe e nder Aljannaaji Neemii…ói"
  22,57,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe, …ďe fenni kadi Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďen …óon no woodani …ďe lepte hoynooje"
  22,58,"∆Āen feru…ďe e Laawol Alla refti …ďe waraa maa…óum …ďe maayi Alla arsikoyay …ďe arsike mo∆ī∆īo. Pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni …ďuri Mo∆ī∆īude Arsikoo…ďe"
  22,59,"Ma O naadoy…ďe naatirgal ngal …ďe welaa …óum. Pellet, Alla ko O Anndu…óo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  22,60,"∆äum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], kala leptu…óo yeru ko o leptaa kon, refti bewaa e hoore-makko ma Alla wallu mo. Pellet, Alla ko O Yaafotoo…óo Surroowo"
  22,61,"∆äum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], ko fii pellet, Alla hiMo naada jemma on e nder √Īalorma on, hiMo naada kadi √Īalorma on e nder jemma on. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo Yi'oowo"
  22,62,"∆äum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo], ko fii pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga kan pellet, kon ko …ďe noddata gaanin Makko ko …óum woni meere nden. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Toowu…óo Mawnu…óo On"
  22,63,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema Alla O jippinii ndiyam immorde ka kammu, leydi ndin wonti hecci…óundi? Pellet, Alla ko O Newii…óo Humpitii…óo"
  22,64,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Galo Yettinii…óo On"
  22,65,"Enee, a tinaali wonndema Alla eltani on ko woni kon ka leydi, laa…óe …óen no dogira ka maaje Yamaruyee Makko on, hiMo jogitii kammu ngun fii wata ngu yanu e hoore leydi ndin si wonaa e duŇčayee Makko. Pellet, Alla ko O newanii…óo yim…ďe …ďen Yurmtee…óo […ďe]"
  22,66,Ko Kanko woni On wurnu…óo on refiti O wara on refti O wurnitoya on. Pellet ne…ó…óanke on ko o heewu…óo geddi
  22,67,"Men wa…óanii kala mofte laawol ngol …ďe rewata e mu'un, wata …ďe poo…óondir e maa…óa e fiyaake on, noddu faade ka Joomi maa…óa. Pellet, an hi…óa e hoore Laawol Focciingol"
  22,68,"Si …ďe wennjii ma, Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo ko golloton kon"
  22,69,Alla √Ďaaway hakkunde mo'on √Ďalnde Darngal fii kon ko luutondirton fii mu'un
  22,70,"Enee, a anndaali wonndema Alla hiMo Anndi ko woni kon ka kammu e ka leydi, pellet, …óum no e nder Deftere. Pellet, …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] no newanii Alla"
  22,71,"Hi…ďe rewa gaanin Alla kon ko Dalil jippinaaka e fii mu'un, e kon ko ganndal alanaa …ďe e mu'un. Alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen walloowo"
  22,72,"Si jannganaama …ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen …ďanngu…óe a annday e geece …ďen yeddu…ďe mettinaare hi…ďe …óe…ďa yanude e …ďen jannganay…ďe …ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Maaku: \"Yo mi habru on ko …ďuri bonde e …óum moo…óon [ko jaŇčtana…óon kon] ko Yiite ngen Alla fodii nge …ďen yeddu…ďe bonii ruttorde"
  22,73,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, misal piyaama jentee ngal, pellet …ďen …ďe noddoton gaanin Alla, …ďe tagaa hay coongil, hay sinndo …ďe moo…ďondiriino fii …óum. Si coongil(mbuubu)ngil jattii …ďe go…ó…óum …ďe hattantaake ja…ďtugol ngil …óum. ∆äa…ď…ďu…óo on e …óa…ď…ďaa…óo on fow no lo'i"
  22,74,"∆Āe mawniniraali Alla no O haani Mawninirde non. Pellet, Alla ko O Dolnu…óo Teddu…óo"
  22,75,"Alla no su…ďoo immorde e Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen Nulaa…ďe e yim…ďe …ďen kadi. Pellet, Alla ko O Nanoowo Yi'oowo"
  22,76,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso ma…ď…ďe e ko woni kon hedde …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, ko faade ka Alla fiyakuuji …óin ruttetee"
  22,77,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óin…ďe, Ru∆ī∆īee Sujjon Rewon Joomi mo'on, gollon ko mo∆ī∆īi kon belajo'o onon on maloyte"
  22,78,"Wa…óiree Jihaadi fii Alla no Jihaadi haaniri non, Kanko O Su…ďike on O wa…óanaali on …ďitteende ka nder Diina, Diina baaba moo…óon Ibraahiima ko Kanko inni on jul…ďe ko adii [ndee Alqur'aanaare] e nder mayre kadi, fii yo Nulaa…óo on laato seedo e hoore-mo'on onon kadi wonon seeditoytoo…ďe e hoore yim…ďe …ďen. √Ďii…ďnee e Julde nden totton Jakka on jogitee Alla, ko Kanko woni Gi…óo moo…óon mo∆ī∆īii gi…óo mo∆ī∆īii walloowo on"